skins.shipDescription: New Orleans-class heavy cruiser C Vincennes, hull number CA-44.
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm Vincennes, New Orleans-class heavy cruiser number 7. I've been to lots of places and given it my all in many battles... The last one I remember was at Savo Island...
skins.acquisition: I'm Vincennes of the New Orleans-class... Commander, don't you want to take me home?
skins.details: Wanna space out and stare at the clouds?
skins.secretaryIdle1: Because my sisters like to take care of everything for me, my primary responsibility is spacing out.
skins.secretaryIdle2: My sisters gave me way too many snacks... Commander, wanna help me out?
skins.secretaryIdle3: So bored... Commander, let's do something together... like spacing out...
skins.secretaryTouch: Commander... can you guess what I'm thinking right now?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Woah?! Commander, what are you doing?!

skins.details: I like dreaming. There are no missions... or fighting... or sorrows...
skins.secretaryIdle1: In my dreams, everyone can play together happily...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Zzz... the donut monster... is gonna catch me... zzz...
skins.secretaryIdle3: Mr. Meowy got so big... zzz...
skins.secretaryTouch: Astoria... don't shake me please... Zzz...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Zzz... Ahh... donut monster... not right there... Commander, save meee... zzz....

skins.shipDescription: Off to school we go~ Being punctual makes me a good girl~
skins.acquisition: Off to school we go~ Being punctual makes me a good girl~
skins.details: A photo op? Sure... Lemme make a pose~
skins.secretaryIdle1: What did I learn in class? Dunno... the clouds outside looked really neat...
skins.secretaryIdle2: I saw a black cat on the way to school this morning... Wonder if it's some kind of omen?
skins.secretaryIdle3: Why isn't there some class just for spacing out...
skins.secretaryTouch: Are you here to sit in, Commander?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Nyahh! Th-this is a violation of school rules!
